{"tid":612752,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無神探伽利略同好??","createTime":"2018-04-01T06:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T08:15:31.000Z","uid":175233,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb055f975f0e85575415c9486db2f6a5943303e2","tid":612752,"uid":175233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"本身唔係咁好日本電視劇，個陣TVB播緊神探伽利略，得閒就望兩眼，點知返唔到轉頭，福山雅治作為物理科副教授，用物理角度去破案，真係型到爆，雖然佢係套劇裡面好chok⋯⋯身為理科L的我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個陣一口氣睇曬成套嘢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想睇睇有無神探伽利略同好，而且想問下各位巴打絲打有無類似這一類型的片睇，真係好鬼正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/140846_cf9e34eb26614f0a8501336bcb4bf72c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F140846_cf9e34eb26614f0a8501336bcb4bf72c.png&h=e5932f91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/140847_946559dc658eb208cdc2996f41e29e67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F140847_946559dc658eb208cdc2996f41e29e67.png&h=562321ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"404b545d192d40996bdf0f85a0da7a626e269161","tid":612752,"uid":40170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"就係因為想聽得明柴咲幸原聲去學日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef16c